	  at org.apache.shardingsphere.transaction.xa.XAShardingSphereTransactionManager.newXATransactionDataSource(XAShardingSphereTransactionManager.java:62)
```

I had a short look at Atomikos [Release Notes](https://www.atomikos.com/Main/ReleaseNotes) and [TransactionsEssentials 5.0](https://www.atomikos.com/Blog/TransactionsEssentials5dot0), it need more investigation of upgrading atomikos version.

Upgrade atomikos may be the easiest way, I'm considering other ways too.
